name: FI (19)
description:
This 2-vehicle crash occurred on an undivided and level roadway. This roadway consists of 2 lanes in each direction with parking lanes on both sides. In the precrash area, the southbound lanes are curved to the left (the radius of curvature is 375 meters). The speed limit on this roadway is 40 kmph (25 mph). This crash occurred during daylight hours with no adverse atmospheric conditions.
vehicle1 (vehicle1), a vehicle1, was southbound in lane 1. vehicle2 (vehicle2), a vehicle2, was parked on the right (west) side of the southbound roadway. vehicle1 traveled to the right and the front struck the back of vehicle2. vehicle1 was towed due to damage.
